sectionOne.title: History
sectionOne.subTitle: Zede Digital Agency was founded in 2020 as a one-man internet consulting firm.
sectionOne.paragraph: Today, Duduk has growninto a full-fledged internet marketing firm with services including website development, graphic design, internet marketing and website support.
